= Story Guide =

'''Final Fantasy IV''' tells the story of Cecil, a Dark Knight seeking redemption.

__TOC__

== Premise ==

Cecil Harvey, captain of Baron's Red Wings airship fleet, questions his king's orders after attacking the innocent village of Mysidia to steal their Crystal. This begins his journey of redemption.

== Part 1: Cecil's Doubts ==

=== Baron Intro ===

* Cecil returns from Mysidia with the Water Crystal
* Questions his orders
* King strips him of command
* Sent to deliver a package to Mist Village

=== Mist Destruction ===

* Travel through Mist Cave (Mist Dragon boss)
* Package contains Bomb Ring
* Village destroyed
* Rydia's mother dies
* Cecil protects Rydia

=== Desert Journey ===

* Escape to Kaipo
* Rosa is sick with desert fever
* Need SandRuby from Antlion's Den
* Edward joins party
* Cure Rosa

== Part 2: Gathering Allies ==

=== Mt. Hobs ===

* Reach Fabul through mountains
* Yang joins after ice blocks
* Mom Bomb boss

=== Fabul Defense ===

* Defend Fabul Castle
* Kain has turned traitor
* Golbez takes the Crystal
* Rosa kidnapped
* Party aboard ship, then attacked

=== Mysidia ===

* Wash ashore in Mysidia
* Must atone for crimes
* Elder sends Cecil to Mt. Ordeals
* Palom and Porom join

=== Mt. Ordeals ===

* Climb the mountain
* Face past as Dark Knight
* Become a Paladin
* Learn true history
* Tellah recovers Meteo spell

== Part 3: Rescue Rosa ==

=== Magnetic Cave ===

* Travel to Troia
* Dark Elf has Earth Crystal
* Edward's harp breaks spell
* Recover Crystal

=== Tower of Zot ===

* Trade Crystal for Rosa
* Climb the tower
* Face the Magus Sisters
* Golbez wounded by Tellah's Meteo
* Tellah dies
* Rescue Rosa
* Kain breaks free temporarily

=== Return to Baron ===

* Retake Baron Castle
* Defeat Cagnazzo (water fiend)
* Palom and Porom petrify to save party
* Gain Enterprise airship

== Part 4: The Underworld ==

=== Underground ===

* Enter the Underworld via Agart
* Meet Dwarven King Giott
* Tower of Bab-il rises
* Battles with Dr. Lugae and Rubicante

=== Edge's Quest ===

* Meet Edge in Eblan Cave
* His parents transformed into monsters
* Edge joins party

=== The Crystals ===

* Race for the remaining Crystals
* Dark Crystals and Light Crystals
* Golbez collecting them all

=== Sealed Cave ===

* Retrieve final Dark Crystal
* Kain (controlled again) steals it
* All eight Crystals taken

== Part 5: The Moon ==

=== Giant of Bab-il ===

* Giant robot activated
* Allies from throughout journey help
* Board the Giant
* Defeat elements inside
* Golbez and Kain freed from control
* Golbez is Cecil's brother

=== Lunar Journey ===

* Travel to the Moon via Big Whale
* Meet FuSoYa
* Learn of Zemus, true villain
* Cecil is half-Lunarian

=== Lunar Subterrane ===

* Final dungeon
* Boss gauntlet
* Optional summons (Bahamut)
* Reach Zemus's chamber

=== Final Battle ===

* Golbez and FuSoYa confront Zemus
* Cast Twin Meteo
* Zemus transforms to Zeromus
* Golbez and FuSoYa defeated
* Cecil's party takes over
* Prayer from all allies enables Big Bang survival
* Defeat Zeromus

== Ending ==

* Return to Earth
* Multiple character epilogues
* Cecil and Rosa marry
* Crowned King and Queen of Baron
* Peace restored

